author: Jonathan Sawyer
title: Ty Dolla $ign Joins Lecrae in New Video For “Blessings”
text:
While currently prepping his forthcoming eighth LP, Grammy Award-winning rapper Lecrae this week delivers the official music video for hit single “Blessings” featuring crooner Ty Dolla $ign . 
Dolla $ign joins Lecrae in the aesthetic, which highlights the pair of hip-hop artists performing the collaborative tune at a family function. As you can gather from the title of the song, it’s all about counting those blessings. 
In speaking on Ty and the joint work, the Christian rapper revealed to Rolling Stone : “I had just been a fan of his work then I came to find out he was a mutual fan of my work. I sent him a couple records. He liked some of them, and ‘Blessings’ was the one that stuck.”
“Blessings” will appear on Lecrae’s upcoming album, due out later this year. 
For more music, see below to watch NAV lose himself in a trippy purple haze in “Myself.”
